snippet.title: Diana Dress Up in Princess and Playing With Toys
snippet.description:
Diana wants to be a Princess. She dresses up in a dress and goes to buy toys. But on the way with the Princess Carriage there are troubles. Brother Roma comes to the rescue in time ... Kids playing with toys.
